	<H4>Bela Emerson's 2 x 120 at Leigh Folk Festival, 28th June '15</H4>
	
	<p>Bela Emerson invites the audience to become co-creators: this thirty-five minute piece connects a series of spontaneous interactions between Emerson and audience, who are invited to play with her for two minutes each. Participants are offered one of three specific approaches to generate a unique collaborative flow of sound. Drawing together Emersons extensive experience as both improviser and community musician, this is audacious and inclusive work.<br><br>http://www.lovesouthend.co.uk/event/leigh-folk-festival-2015</p>
	<BR>
	<p></p>
</LI>

