	<p>Bela Emerson is now co-director of Open Strings Music, a not-for-profit organisation set up to help people of all abilities and ages explore and create music together.<br><br></p><p><a href="http://www.openstrings.co.uk"><b> Open Strings Musics website</b></a> </p><br></p><p><a href="http://www.facebook.com/openstringsmusic"><b> Connect with us on facebook here</b></a> </p></p>
