	<p>Near Wanstonia is a full-length track by Baby (ex-Vole, ex-ViV; Bela Emerson contributes) which was recorded by a road built in east London in the 1990s: Wanstonia was a 'free state' set up by environmental activists along the proposed route.<br><br>Preview here: http://www.babbby.com/nearwanstonia/ & launch on 9th December at 491</p>
