	<H4>[reciprocess : +/vs.] compilation nominated for Qwartz 2010 award</H4>
	
	<p>Philippe Petit (BiP_HOp)s collaborative compilation, originally released as an accompaniment to The Wire magazine in March 09, has been nominated for Best Compilation of the Year category of the prestigious Qwartz Electronic Music Awards.The compilation features Petits collaborations with a wide variety of musicians, including Bela Emerson, Douglas Benford, Cosey Fanni Tutti, Lydia Lunch, &amp; Simon Fisher Turner.Voting is still open; hear all the nominations at <a href="http://www.qwartz.org/index.php?/Edition-6/Qwartz-6-Compilation/menu-id-118.html" target="_blank">Qwartz Electronic Music Awards - Qwartz 6 - Compilation</a></p>
	<BR>
	<p></p>
