	<H4>Bela Emerson & Carlos Vera (US) at Coachwerks, 20th October 09</H4>
	
	<p>Hot on the heels of their packed-out show at Amiens Nuit Blanche, Bela & Carlos perform their only UK date, in Brighton on Tuesday 20th. Using cello, effects, canvas and paintbrushes, they will create an improvised intermedia performance that has already been described as spellbinding. The evening opens with a live music/visuals set from Kopek (www.myspace.com/kopekmusic) & an enchanting storytelling performance from Say Bon.</p>
	<BR>
	<p></p>
